--[[
    ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
    ║            SECRET CHAT - LocalScript             ║
    ║  Only players running this exact script can      ║
    ║  see and send messages in the secret channel.    ║
    ║                                                  ║
    ║  HOW TO USE:                                     ║
    ║    • Press ['] (apostrophe) to open/close        ║
    ║    • Type your message and press Enter or Send   ║
    ║    • Only other script users will see it         ║
    ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

    SETUP:
      Place this LocalScript inside StarterPlayerScripts.
      The SECRET_TAG below must be IDENTICAL in every copy
      of the script — change it to make your own private channel.
--]]

